{"title_page": "Pol van Boekel", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2013}}\n{{Infobox football official\n| name            = Pol van Boekel\n| image           = Pol van Boekel.jpg\n| caption         = Pol van Boekel (center) in 2008\n| full_name       = Paulus Hendrikus Martinus van Boekel\n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1975|9|19|df=y}}\n| birth_place     = [[Venray]], [[Netherlands]]\n| death_date      = \n| death_place     = \n| years1          = \n| league1         = [[Eredivisie]]\n| role1           = Referee\n| internationalyears1 = 2008\u2013\n| confederation1      = [[FIFA]] listed\n| internationalrole1  = Referee\n}}\n\n'''Paulus Hendrikus Martinus \"Pol\" van Boekel''' (born 19 September 1975) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] international [[Referee (association football)|referee]], who refereed at the [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification (UEFA)|2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]],<ref>[http://worldreferee.com/site/copy.php?linkID=1072&linkType=referee&contextType=bio Profile]</ref> beginning with the match between [[Moldova national football team|Moldova]] and [[England national football team|England]].<ref>FIFA. [https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/europe/matches/round=258374/match=300182319/report.html \"Match Report - Moldova - England 0:5 (0:3)\"]. 7 September 2012. Retrieved on 23 May 2013.</ref>\n\nVan Boekel became a [[FIFA International Referees List|FIFA]] referee in 2008.<ref>FIFA. [https://www.fifa.com/associations/association=ned/footballofficials/referees/peoplekind=ref.html \"Netherlands: Referees\"]. Retrieved on 23 May 2013.</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Boekel, Pol van}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Dutch football referees]]\n[[Category:People from Venray]]\n[[Category:VVV-Venlo players]]\n[[Category:Association footballers not categorized by position]]\n[[Category:Dutch footballers]]\n\n\n{{Netherlands-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2013}}\n{{Infobox football official\n| officialname    = Pol van Boekel\n| image           = Pol van Boekel.jpg\n| fullname        = Paulus Hendrikus Martinus van Boekel\n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1975|9|19|df=y}}\n| birth_place     = [[Venray]], [[Netherlands]]\n| death_date      = \n| death_place     = \n| years1          = \n| league1         = [[Eredivisie]]\n| role1           = Referee\n| internationalyears1 = 2008\u2013\n| confederation1      = [[FIFA]] listed\n| internationalrole1  = Referee\n}}\n'''Paulus Hendrikus Martinus \"Pol\" van Boekel''' (born 19 September 1975) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] international [[Referee (association football)|referee]], who refereed at the [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification (UEFA)|2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]],<ref>[http://worldreferee.com/site/copy.php?linkID=1072&linkType=referee&contextType=bio Profile]</ref> beginning with the match between [[Moldova national football team|Moldova]] and [[England national football team|England]].<ref>FIFA. [https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/europe/matches/round=258374/match=300182319/report.html \"Match Report - Moldova - England 0:5 (0:3)\"]. 7 September 2012. Retrieved on 23 May 2013.</ref>\n\nVan Boekel became a [[FIFA International Referees List|FIFA]] referee in 2008.<ref>FIFA. [https://www.fifa.com/associations/association=ned/footballofficials/referees/peoplekind=ref.html \"Netherlands: Referees\"]. Retrieved on 23 May 2013.</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Boekel, Pol van}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Dutch football referees]]\n[[Category:People from Venray]]\n[[Category:VVV-Venlo players]]\n[[Category:Association footballers not categorized by position]]\n[[Category:Dutch footballers]]\n{{Netherlands-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "update infobox to remove article from unknown parameter category", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pol_van_Boekel